comment: RATR shows that Gortat (WAS) clamps the arm of Curry (GSW) while setting the screen.
Green (GSW) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Beal (WAS) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Green (GSW) sets the screen on Porter Jr. (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Livingston (GSW) makes body to body contact with Beal (WAS) that affects his SQBR.
[Incidental or immaterial] Wall (WAS) grabs Curry's (GSW) jersey but the contact does not affect his FOM.
Green (GSW) sets the screen on Wall (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Morris (WAS) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Curry (GSW) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) makes contact to Porter Jr.'s (WAS) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Green (GSW) makes contact to Morris' (WAS) arm that affects his SQBR.
